title: United Kingdom Imports of Products of Animal Origin Nie
description: Imports of Products of Animal Origin Nie in the United Kingdom increased to 17.23 GBP Million in September from 17.11 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Products of Animal Origin Nie in the United Kingdom averaged 9.31 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 18.73 GBP Million in May of 2018 and a record low of 4.56 GBP Million in September of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Products of Animal Origin Nie.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
